      "body" : "In Debian Wheezy, you can add \"oldstable\" to your aptitude streams is sources.list, it contains libdb4.8-dev and libdb4.8++-dev. Simply add this line to the file:\r\n\r\ndeb http://[your debian package url]/debian/ oldstable main contrib non-free\r\n\r\nThen do an update and install the packages as usual.",
